- Empat. Putar pinggangmu, dua, tiga.
- Bagus.

155
00:08:42,731 --> 00:08:43,940
Bagus. Dua.

156
00:08:44,024 --> 00:08:46,401
JAKSA CHOI MYUNG-HEE

157
00:08:48,069 --> 00:08:51,239
Yang terhormat,
Bapak Wakil Menteri Lee Nam-su.

